Package: indRect
Type: Package
Title: Visualize Indirect Effects in Causal Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Allen", "Bush-BeauprÃ©", , "allen.bush-beaupre@usherbrooke.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for visualizing direct and indirect effects in causal models.
    Provides functions to extract model predictions and create publication-ready
    plots showing indirect effects through mediator variables. Supports simple
    mediation, interacting predictors, and interaction as mediator use cases.
